| Logic 32          | Institutional memory reinforces daily reliance         |

---

# 9Ô∏è‚É£ STRATEGIC OUTCOMES

* Platform becomes the **default workflow tool** for procurement teams
* Daily habits reduce cognitive friction in adoption
* Behavioral lock-in complements institutional memory lock-in (Logic 32)
* Switching platforms feels disruptive and costly

