Procurement Activity ‚Üí Workflow Capture ‚Üí Usage Analytics ‚Üí Habit Formation ‚Üí Lock-In Measurement
```

---

# üî∑ POSITION IN THE SYSTEM

Logic 33 sits at the **behavioral lock-in layer**, strengthening platform retention by:

* Leveraging institutional memory (Logic 32)
* Reinforcing data-driven recommendations (Logic 31)
* Embedding day-to-day operational dependency for buyers

It ensures that **adoption becomes a habit, not just a policy**.
